  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to assess the value of adding 3D power Doppler (as a diagnostic
      technique) to gray scale technique in the antenatal diagnosis of morbidly adherent placenta
      as well as predict the surgical outcome regarding the type of surgery and the intra operative
      morbidities.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
